### Summary Table

| # | Hazard | Location | Severity | Currently Triggered? |
|---|--------|----------|----------|----------------------|
| 1 | `nextIndex++` non-atomicity (task factory yield) | `runConcurrent` | Low | No — factories are sync |
| 2 | Sparse `results` array on unguarded throws | `runConcurrent` | Low | No — tasks are all try-caught |
| 3 | `Promise.all` abandons in-flight tasks on worker-loop throw | `runConcurrent` | Medium | No — worker loop can't throw today |
| 4 | Schema resolution throws before `onToolCall` fires | `run_subcalls` | Low | Yes — by design, tested |
| 5 | `startMs` shadowing silently picks up wrong timestamp if inner is removed | `run_subcalls` | Medium | No — both `startMs` exist today |
